       MACRO
        SETM  &I
.***THIS MACRO ISSUES A BMS INSTRUCTION TO SET 31 BIT ADDRESSING
.***ON OR OFF: SETM ON    SETM  OFF
        AIF ('&I' EQ 'OFF').OFF
        AIF ('&I' EQ 'ON').ON
         MEXIT
.OFF     ANOP
         SR  1,1
          LA  1,*+6
         BSM  0,1
         MEXIT
.ON      ANOP
          LA  1,*+10
          ICM  1,8,=X'80'
         BSM  0,1
         MEXIT
         MEND
